Paper: hep-th/0203248

Date: 2002-03-26

Title: Conformal Field Theory for the Superstring in a Ramond-Ramond Plane Wave

BackgroundComments: 13 pages harvmac

Journal-ref: JHEP 0204 (2002) 037

A quantizable worldsheet action is constructed for the superstring in asupersymmetric plane wave background with Ramond-Ramond flux. The action ismanifestly invariant under all isometries of the background and is an exactworldsheet conformal field theory.